Why do we hire you ?

This is one of the most frequently asked question in company's interview question. This question is a big opportunity
to highlight your skills and showing to them how innovative and productive you are for them and bring change for 
goodness and bring something new to them. Also give an example while explaining your skills.
Your leadership quality , initiator quality make them to feel good if you tell them with an example.

Like I help my classmate in study as he was facing bad time in his life.

or If you are experienced then you can say that I help my colleague in a project as he is legging behind
from our teammates due to communication gap. 

